"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sif1665702784304.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sif1665702784304.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sif1665702784304.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sif1665702784304\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sif1665702784304__topic_d144065e1_d144066e1_d144067e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144068e1_d144069e1_d144070e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> }\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">URL</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sif1665702784304__section_pwx_phn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685855e64\">Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144074e1_d144075e1_d144076e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">URL</var>—URL that is used as the base\n            URL for locating the Uniface runtime files.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sif1665702784304__section_e5f_rhn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685855e75\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sif1665702784304__table_d17447e1_d17448e1_d17449e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[WEB]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">../common</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sif1665702784304__section_zs2_5hn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685855e123\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144083e1_d144084e1_d144085e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span>\n            is defined, Uniface uses this to construct semantic URLs in the HTML\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">link</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">script</code> definitions in the generated DSP\n            page.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144086e1_d144087e1_d144088e1\">If no URL is specified, Uniface uses\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">../common</code> as the base URL.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144089e1_d144090e1_d144091e1\">This URL can be referenced by the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LIBURL</code> expression in the URLs for CSS and JavaScript files. For\n            example, the CSS widget property can specify a CSS file as:\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LIBURL/css/syntaxerrors.css</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sif1665702784304__section_x1p_whn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685855e156\">Example:  Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144095e1_d144096e1_d144097e1\">For example, if\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span> is not defined, the HTML generated for a\n            DSP includes the following URL paths for loading JavaScript and CSS resources:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sif1665702784304__pre_ks3_yhn_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/uwindow/uwindow.css\" /&gt;\n &lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/ubusyindicator/ubusyindicator.css\" /&gt;\n &lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/uapplayout.css\" /&gt;\n ...\n &lt;script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../common/uniface.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n ...\n </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144098e1_d144099e1_d144100e1\">If you set\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span> in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span>\n            file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sif1665702784304__pre_tq3_yhn_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[WEB]\n$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL = http://my.cdn/uniface</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sif1665702784304__p_d144101e1_d144102e1_d144103e1\">The resulting HTML page contains the following\n            URLs:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"sif1665702784304__pre_dq3_yhn_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/uwindow/uwindow.css\" /&gt;\n &lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/ubusyindicator/ubusyindicator.css\" /&gt;\n &lt;link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/uapplayout.css\" /&gt;\n ...\n &lt;script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/uniface.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n ...\n </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgz1665703061446.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>CSS</a><p>DSP widget property that specifies one or more CSS files that are required to style the DSP widget.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531995\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531995\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located. $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL { = } URL Values URL —URL that is used as the base URL for locating the Uniface runtime files. Defaults Assignment file: wasv.asn Section: [WEB] Default value: ../common Description When $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL is defined, Uniface uses this to construct semantic URLs in the HTML link and script definitions in the generated DSP page. If no URL is specified, Uniface uses ../common as the base URL. This URL can be referenced by the $LIBURL expression in the URLs for CSS and JavaScript files. For example, the CSS widget property can specify a CSS file as: $LIBURL/css/syntaxerrors.css . Example: Using $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL For example, if $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL is not defined, the HTML generated for a DSP includes the following URL paths for loading JavaScript and CSS resources: <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/uwindow/uwindow.css\" /> <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/ubusyindicator/ubusyindicator.css\" /> <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../common/css/uapplayout.css\" /> ... <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../common/uniface.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script> ... Copy If you set $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL in the wasv.asn file: [WEB] $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL = http://my.cdn/uniface Copy The resulting HTML page contains the following URLs: <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/uwindow/uwindow.css\" /> <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/ubusyindicator/ubusyindicator.css\" /> <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/css/uapplayout.css\" /> ... <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://my.cdn/uniface/uniface.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script> ... Copy Related Links CSS DSP widget property that specifies one or more CSS files that are required to style the DSP widget. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}